com.gwtplatform.mvp.client.annotations

Annotation Type DefaultGatekeeper


  • @Target(value={METHOD,TYPE})
public @interface DefaultGatekeeper
    Use this annotation in your custom ginjector to annotate a method returning a Gatekeeper-derived class. This class will be used to provide places for proxies that are not annotated with the UseGatekeeper annotation.
